title: Live at 5: Washington vs. Rapid City Stevens
text:
Live at 5: Washington vs. Rapid City Stevens Argus Leader Staff 7:44 a.m. CDT October 16, 2015 Washington's Jack Schelhaas carries the ball against Pierre during their game at Howard Wood Field on Oct. 1, 2015. (Photo: Jay Pickthorn - Argus Leader) 
Watch two high school football games, get updates and share your own at ArgusLeader.com tonight. 
Watch Washington vs. Rapid City Stevens below. 
#arguspreps: Add your updates directly in the chat under the video or by adding #arguspreps to your tweets. 
Tailgate: Going to the game? Join our Tailgate Tour when it stops at Howard Wood Field at 5 o'clock to meet our reporter, chat with other fans, enjoy free popcorn and maybe win a $25 gift card.
